          "target": "un pomo rubie",
          "roman": "un pomo rubie",
          "english": "a red apple",
          "note": "Adjectives usually follow the noun.",
          "ipa": "un pˈomo rˈubje",
          "audio": "audio/un-pomo-rubie.wav"
        }
      ],
      "grammar": {
        "title": "Invariable adjectives",
        "body": "Adjectives never change for gender or number:\n| un pomo rubie | a red apple |\n| duo pomos rubie | two red apples |\n| un casa rubie | a red house |\nThey normally follow the noun (pomo rubie), though short common ones may precede it (un bon idea)."
      }
    },
